== Umwuga ==
ISHIMWE CLAUDETTE w’imyaka 17  ubarizwa mu ikipe ya Cercle Sportif Karongi yitabiriye imikino Nyafurika y’umukino wo koga yiswe “14th CANA AFRICA SWIMMING CHAMPIONSHIP” yabereye muri Ghana taliki 11 kugeza 16 Ukwakira 2021 akoresha amasegonda 46 n’ibice 90 mu koga metero 50.<ref>http://www.impamba.com/2021/12/16/koga-ishimwe-claudette-yatangiye-aba-uwa-mbere-muri-shampiyona-yisi/</ref>Ishimwe usanzwe abarizwa muri Cercle Sportif de Karongi, ni umwe mu bakinnyi barindwi bakoze amakosa yatumye ibihe bari bakoresheje biteshwa agaciro mu masibo (heats) umunani yakinnye ku wa Kane.

